</head>
	<body>
		<div class="content">
			<div id="description">
				<center><h2>Service Level Agreement</h2></center>
				<p>
					This agreement represents a service level agreement SLA for the
					provisioning of IT services required to support and sustain user
					request.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p>
					The following service provider (s) and customer (s) will be used as
					the basis of the agreement and represent the primary stakeholders
					associated with this SLA.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p><span>IT Service Provider(s) :</span>Azure</p>
				<br />
				<p><span>IT Customer(s) :</span>Sara</p>
				<br />
				<p>The service covered by this agreement is:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Tax Accounting service</li>
				</ul>
				<br />
				<p>With functional functionality Tax accounting.</p>
				<br />
				<p>The quality of service (QoS) information are listed as follows:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Price : 3.0 euros/month.</li>
					<li>Rating: 4.5.</li>
					<li>Availability :99%.</li>
				</ul>
				<br />
				<p>
					This contract will take effect (01/07/2022) and end (01/12/2022). In
					the event of delay, the service provider must inform the customer as
					quickly as possible.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p>
					The service provider undertakes to carry out the mission entrusted in
					the rules of the art. For this, it will mobilize all the necessary
					means, while respecting the regulations in force.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p>
					For his part, the Customer must provide the service provider with all
					the information that will be useful to carry out their mission.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p>
					The customer must pay the service provider the sum of
					<span>3.3 euros/month</span>, paid as follows:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Price of service is :<span>3.0 euros/month</span>.</li>
				</ul>
				<br />
				<p>
					CloudBroker share of the payment represents 10% of the total price,
					or
					<span>0.3 euro/month</span>. The total price of the service after
					adding CloudBroker share is: <span>3.3 euros/month</span>.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p>
					In the event of late payment, penalties of an amount will be applied.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p>
					The service provider also undertakes not to disclose any confidential
					information relating to the customer.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p>
					If you agree to the terms of this SLA select (I accept) in the choices
					below.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="radio">
				<div class="rat"><input type="radio" /><label>I accept</label></div>
				<div class="rat"><input type="radio" /><label>I decline</label></div>
			</div>	
			
		</div>

	</body>
</html>
